      <title>胡塞武装表示，如果以色列停止“侵略”，他们可以重新评估红海袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-they-can-reassess-red-sea-attacks-if-israeli-aggression-stops-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装周二表示，一旦以色列结束对加沙地带的“侵略”，他们只能重新考虑对红海国际航运的导弹和无人机袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthis-say-they-can-reassess-red-sea-attacks-if-israeli-aggression-stops-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:36:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到渥太华的审查，中国资金仍在追逐加拿大的重要矿业交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-money-still-chasing-canadian-critical-mining-deals-despite-ottawas-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据阿尔伯塔大学进行的专有研究，加拿大收紧关键矿产行业的外国投资规则一年后，中国资金继续涌入多伦多上市的矿业公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-money-still-chasing-canadian-critical-mining-deals-despite-ottawas-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国反对派人物将为党的生存而“竭尽全力”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-opposition-leader-will-fight-tooth-nail-partys-survival-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国反对党领袖、前总理候选人周二表示，在法律威胁下，他的前进党将为其未来“竭尽全力”，法律威胁可能导致该支持改革组织解散，其领导人被禁止参政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-opposition-leader-will-fight-tooth-nail-partys-survival-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国称朝鲜已向俄罗斯运送6,700个集装箱弹药</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-has-sent-6700-containers-munitions-russia-south-korea-says-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国媒体周二援引国防部长的话称，自 7 月以来，朝鲜已向俄罗斯运送了约 6,700 个集装箱，载有数百万弹药，以支持其对乌克兰的战争，这表明朝鲜正在进行武器转让。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-has-sent-6700-containers-munitions-russia-south-korea-says-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 08:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦以贪污罪起诉被监禁的前总理汗及其妻子</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-indicted-graft-case-geo-news-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦一家法院周二对前总理伊姆兰·汗和他的第三任妻子布什拉·比比提出起诉，指控他们在担任总理期间滥用职权收受土地贿赂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-wife-indicted-graft-case-geo-news-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 08:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴旗下南亚电商巨头Daraz在备忘录中宣布裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴旗下电子商务平台 Daraz Group 代理首席执行官 James Dong 周二在路透社看到的一份致员工的内部备忘录中表示，该公司已宣布对整个集团进行裁员，以“采用更加精简和灵活的结构”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着人口问题加深，日本2023年新生儿出生率降至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/number-births-japan-hits-record-low-2023-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二公布的政府初步数据显示，2023 年日本出生婴儿数量连续第八年下降，创历史新低，突显该国在遏制人口减少方面面临的艰巨任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/number-births-japan-hits-record-low-2023-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚贸易部长表示，中国葡萄酒争端可能在几周内得到解决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚贸易部长唐·法雷尔周二表示，与中国有关澳大利亚葡萄酒关税的贸易争端可能“在几周内”得到解决，从而消除了限制其对华出口的最后障碍之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>悉尼同性恋狂欢节要求警察不要在警察被指控谋杀后游行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydney-gay-mardi-gras-asks-police-not-march-after-officer-accused-murders-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一名现职警察被指控谋杀两名同性恋男子后，澳大利亚警方正在与悉尼举世闻名的同性恋狂欢节游行的组织者进行谈判，以决定是否参加本周末的活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydney-gay-mardi-gras-asks-police-not-march-after-officer-accused-murders-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:38:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰将废除世界首个烟草禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/new-zealand-set-scrap-world-first-tobacco-ban-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府表示，新西兰将于周二废除世界上第一部禁止向子孙后代销售烟草的法律，尽管研究人员和活动人士警告人们可能因此而死亡的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/new-zealand-set-scrap-world-first-tobacco-ban-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
